        <updateDate>2015-09-08T20:57:14Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Enhancing Security for Military Personnel Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense (DOD) to: (1) submit to Congress a plan to enhance security of military personnel at DOD installations in the United States; and (2) implement the plan recommendations within 90 days after enactment of this Act, and after briefing Congress.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
